            <h1>Instructions:</h1>
            <p>Click on any of the black dots to learn about a body part of the oyster;<br>Then click next to go on to the game.</p>
			  <p script='font-size: 10px;'>Currently only works on 15 inch screens</p>
            <a href='/play'>
